DESCRIPTION:No script. No plan. And a lucky dip of unexpected\, second-hand
  goodies. Let the silliness begin! Armed with bizarre finds from local char
 ity shops and audience suggestions\, the WIT-Nits create You Shouldn’t Ha
 ve - a hilarious\, anything-can-happen improvised show where every performa
 nce is unique. Woking Improv Theatre’s original house team\, the WIT-Nits
  have been delighting audiences across London and the South East for two ye
 ars\, kicking things off with a burst of fast\, high-energy games before di
 ving into the unexpected. Unpredictable\, unrepeatable and unapologetically
  silly\, You Shouldn't Have!\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atl
 as/event/wit-nits/
